docs.text: our hero is warrant officer paul brenner , a brash investigator for the u . s . army's criminal investigation division .

docs.text: his latest case is the murder of captain elisabeth campbell ( leslie stefanson ) at a georgia base , the victim found tied to the ground after an apparent sexual assault and strangulation .

docs.text: complicating the case is the fact that capt . campbell is the daughter of general joe campbell ( james cromwell ) , a war hero and potential vice-presidential nominee .
